Text: "for the first time I'll go to the Malaysia which is melacca. I have low expected\
  \ than singapore, my another visit in the same year.\nI arrive at KLIA 2 with budget\
  \ air, air asia at the night and because im very perfectionist and planner, I can't\
  \ sleep on the airport and waiting till morning to start my journey. so I booking\
  \ the hotel at the KLIA 2 for sleep in just a hours. \nat the morning, I go to the\
  \ penang with bus from KLIA 2, with my ticket booking by online (redbus), oh one\
  \ thing, Im alone going there. \nWhen im arrive at the penang, oh My God, im falling\
  \ in love with this little city, with dominant red and very interesting.\nhistorical\
  \ city, with culinary delicious too. I love penang, im just a half day at there,\
  \ with walk on my feet take a picture, and going to every building there, to read\
  \ the history was happen there. \nI love going to anywhere country by my self, singapore,\
  \ Thailand (with group), because at there I can push my self to doing anything I\
  \ want, and push my self to be strong than i KNow."
